# 🏥 Hospital Management Analytics Platform using Snowflake

## 📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates an end-to-end Hospital Management Analytics Platform built using Snowflake. The solution ingests patient, appointment, and billing data from AWS S3, processes it through Snowflake Streams and Tasks, applies data quality validations, and delivers secure analytical insights through Dynamic Tables, Views, RBAC, and Masking Policies.

The project follows a modern data warehouse architecture and showcases real-world Snowflake capabilities for data engineering, governance, and analytics.

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

```text
AWS S3
   │
   ▼
External Stage
   │
   ▼
Snowpipe
   │
   ▼
RAW Tables
   │
   ▼
Streams
   │
   ▼
CORE Tables
   │
   ├── Valid Records
   │
   └── Exception Tables
          (Invalid Records)
   │
   ▼
Dynamic Dimension Tables
Dynamic Fact Tables
   │
   ▼
Analytics Views
   │
   ▼
RBAC + Masking Policies
   │
   ▼
Secure Views
   │
   ▼
Power BI Dashboard
```

