## 📈 Analytics Views

### Department Appointment Summary

```text
VW_DEPT_APPT_SUMMARY
```

KPIs:

* Total Appointments
* Completed Visits
* No-Shows
* Completion Rate

### Daily OPD Trend

```text
VW_DAILY_OPD_TREND
```

KPIs:

* Daily Visits
* No-Shows
* Average Appointments per Doctor

### Revenue by Department

```text
VW_REVENUE_BY_DEPT
```

KPIs:

* Gross Revenue
* Net Revenue
* Average Bill Value

### Patient Utilization

```text
VW_PATIENT_UTILIZATION
```

KPIs:

* Total Visits
* Last Visit Date
* Lifetime Revenue

### Insurance Mix

```text
VW_INSURANCE_MIX
```

KPIs:

* Insurance Revenue
* Self-Pay Revenue

---

## 🔐 Security & Governance

### Roles

```text
HOSPITAL_ADMIN_ROLE
HOSPITAL_DOCTOR_ROLE
HOSPITAL_FINANCE_ROLE
```

### Masking Policies

* Patient Name Masking
* Phone Number Masking
* Email Masking
* Revenue Masking
* Insurance Name Masking

### Secure Views

```text
SV_PATIENTS
SV_APPOINTMENTS
SV_BILLING
```

### Row Access Policy

Department-level access control is implemented using Row Access Policies.

